title: Mission Highly Improbable - Part5
info:
ZX Spectrum 48K with AY-interface. 
Soft: ZX SoundTracker 1.1 - the most crude tool ever. ;) And I love it after all, haha.
The song comes from my 2014 chiptune album "Mission Highly Improbable (the ZX-demo original soundtrack)".
All the music in the album comes from “Mission Highly Improbable” demo, released on Forever 2014 Party (came 1st in the ZX demo-compo).
